items.title: Israel strikes southern Beirut on eve of religious holiday
items.description: Israel's military says it was targeting an underground drone factory of armed group Hezbollah.

items.title: Raids across Canary Islands in major cocaine gang bust
items.description: Police say smugglers used a network of speedboats to ferry drugs from South America to the Spanish islands.

items.title: Israeli army admits to Gaza strike after BBC Verify investigation
items.description: At least one Palestinian was killed and 30 others injured in the Israeli strike on tents in Khan Younis on Sunday, medics say.

items.title: Russia launches 'massive' strikes days after Ukrainian drone attack
items.description: Russia's drone and missile attack on Kyiv and other parts on Friday leaves at least three dead.

items.title: North Korea refloats warship after failed launch
items.description: The failed launch drew harsh criticism from Kim Jong Un and led to the arrest of four officials.
